WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.150
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.150 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 18]

01:15.470 --> 01:17.450
No wonder my divination last night warned me

01:18.000 --> 01:19.250
about a backstabber on this trip.

01:27.940 --> 01:28.580
Be cautious.

01:47.000 --> 01:47.530
Xiguang,

01:49.000 --> 01:51.170
the Outcast Tomb

01:51.390 --> 01:53.010
is where demons from overseas are interred.

01:53.520 --> 01:54.730
As they're our enemies,

01:54.910 --> 01:56.450
why bury them formally?

02:00.390 --> 02:00.700
Here.

02:04.160 --> 02:05.860
Because Wuyue Court's elders

02:05.880 --> 02:07.090
are benevolent.

02:07.600 --> 02:09.700
They laid all vanquished monsters

02:10.270 --> 02:12.460
to rest in peace.

02:14.270 --> 02:15.810
Why did Zhuyan sneak in?

02:16.040 --> 02:16.900
Mourning?

02:19.390 --> 02:21.020
Perhaps Demon Lord Yecha's remains

02:21.040 --> 02:22.220
are buried there.

02:23.240 --> 02:25.090
That's why Zhuyan risked everything to get in.

02:29.710 --> 02:30.340
Xiguang,

02:32.200 --> 02:35.340
are Yecha's eyes golden?

02:37.430 --> 02:41.620
Demon Lord Yecha is said to be cruel, bloodthirsty,

02:41.830 --> 02:43.020
and masked,

02:43.040 --> 02:44.180
with blazing golden eyes.

02:44.200 --> 02:44.780
He killed

02:46.080 --> 02:47.020
ruthlessly.

03:23.620 --> 03:25.460
Want a fruit?

03:39.990 --> 03:41.220
School days are long past.

03:43.150 --> 03:43.970
Drop your icy stare

03:44.590 --> 03:45.460
when traveling.

03:45.870 --> 03:46.620
Get along with others.

03:47.080 --> 03:47.570
Got it?

04:02.660 --> 04:05.740
[Xingzheng Hall]

04:27.320 --> 04:27.810
Uncle.

04:28.560 --> 04:29.180
Well done.

04:30.440 --> 04:33.130
Your fire-controlling skill is perfected.

04:34.440 --> 04:36.890
Go into seclusion with me from tomorrow

04:37.960 --> 04:40.980
to cultivate the Hua Sect's advanced inner art.

04:41.830 --> 04:42.420
Seclusion?

04:43.640 --> 04:44.100
I thought

04:44.910 --> 04:46.940
we were going to the Outcast Tomb on the White Cliff.

04:47.960 --> 04:51.860
The tomb was built 500 years ago

04:53.000 --> 04:55.740
by Wuyue Court's ancestors,

04:56.710 --> 04:59.210
deemed useless back then

04:59.640 --> 05:02.100
by other immortal sects.

05:02.590 --> 05:06.500
Now, Cuixuan has summoned all the immortal sects on White Cliff.

05:07.470 --> 05:09.420
Seems disaster looms.

05:10.790 --> 05:12.330
The summons is vague.

05:12.980 --> 05:15.500
A demonic beast is said to have broken into the tomb.

05:16.830 --> 05:17.940
The demon clan

05:19.590 --> 05:21.810
has long lurked,

05:22.700 --> 05:25.370
likely laying traps

05:25.390 --> 05:26.540
for us.

05:27.350 --> 05:28.300
Then anyone going there

05:28.830 --> 05:29.770
will be in danger.

05:30.270 --> 05:32.330
As the Sea Calamity draws near,

05:32.780 --> 05:35.540
all sects are saving their strength,

05:36.460 --> 05:40.940
so few will respond to Wuyue Court.

05:42.830 --> 05:44.060
Cuixuan and his disciples

05:44.580 --> 05:47.060
can handle the demons.

05:47.700 --> 05:49.300
Xingzheng Hall won't step in.

05:50.100 --> 05:51.250
We shall wait and observe.

05:56.830 --> 05:58.300
Lifei has weak spirit power,

05:58.340 --> 05:59.660
and she's not Cuixuan's disciple,

06:00.700 --> 06:01.770
so she probably won't go.

06:34.910 --> 06:36.060
So this is the Outcast Tomb.

06:36.710 --> 06:37.770
What's carved up there?

06:40.030 --> 06:43.300
Outcast Tomb for those from countless states and islands overseas.

06:43.680 --> 06:44.940
Countless states and islands?

06:52.230 --> 06:54.740
Could the traps beyond the Ganhua Realm

06:55.320 --> 06:56.100
be linked to the tomb?

06:58.200 --> 06:59.210
What connection

06:59.910 --> 07:01.250
do those islands have with the demon clan?

07:01.960 --> 07:03.660
They originate from there.

07:04.200 --> 07:05.100
Ancient texts record

07:05.120 --> 07:06.690
that there are countless overseas islands,

07:07.080 --> 07:08.100
each with

07:08.120 --> 07:09.690
unique customs,

07:10.320 --> 07:11.370
swarming with demons.

07:12.710 --> 07:14.660
The texts only mention foreign folk,

07:15.560 --> 07:17.130
not necessarily demons.

07:28.270 --> 07:32.010
The White Cliff is the burial ground of demons,

07:32.350 --> 07:35.450
sealed for centuries after its construction.

07:36.680 --> 07:39.810
Whoever strays will not return.

07:39.830 --> 07:40.980
It's fraught with peril.

07:42.000 --> 07:43.570
This concerns the safety of the Central Plains.

07:44.320 --> 07:45.940
We mustn't take chances.

07:51.590 --> 07:53.770
I will follow you to slay demons,

07:54.000 --> 07:54.810
even at the cost of my life.

07:56.640 --> 07:59.810
I will follow you to slay demons,

08:00.000 --> 08:01.180
even at the cost of my life.

08:31.350 --> 08:32.330
Big trouble!

08:32.910 --> 08:33.810
What's wrong?

08:34.120 --> 08:35.940
I just cast a straw divination for this trip

08:36.230 --> 08:37.300
and got the hexagram Earth Over Mountain, Modesty.

08:37.960 --> 08:39.490
Isn't that an auspicious sign?

08:39.920 --> 08:41.180
It's lucky

08:41.200 --> 08:42.060
anywhere else,

08:42.400 --> 08:43.330
but this is

08:43.800 --> 08:44.570
a graveyard.

08:45.080 --> 08:45.850
Mountains are within this land,

08:46.230 --> 08:47.060
and waters run close beside it.

08:47.660 --> 08:48.300
This means

08:48.800 --> 08:50.020
the truth will surface.

08:50.200 --> 08:51.540
Something huge is going to happen.

08:52.320 --> 08:52.660
Oh!

08:52.660 --> 08:53.420
I need to cast another divination.

08:55.540 --> 08:56.610
Really?

08:58.320 --> 08:58.940
Lifei.

09:00.830 --> 09:01.490
Qin.

09:02.750 --> 09:04.260
Back at Lilie Valley,

09:04.510 --> 09:05.570
I underestimated the enemy

09:06.110 --> 09:07.020
and got corrupted by demonic energy.

09:07.800 --> 09:08.660
Sorry to have offended you.

09:12.540 --> 09:13.420
Please grant me

09:14.080 --> 09:15.690
a chance to make amends.

09:29.630 --> 09:30.380
It's overgrown and deserted.

09:30.990 --> 09:31.690
Let's stick together.

09:46.160 --> 09:46.690
Lifei,

09:47.040 --> 09:48.140
something's odd about the bushes.

09:48.160 --> 09:48.730
Stay close.

09:49.990 --> 09:50.380
Coming.

10:07.110 --> 10:07.610
Don't touch it.

10:08.710 --> 10:09.900
This is Wuyue Court's defensive formation.

10:10.420 --> 10:10.970
Once activated,

10:11.420 --> 10:12.970
it'll attack all intruders without discrimination.

10:16.870 --> 10:18.970
Since when have you two grown so close?

10:57.060 --> 10:59.060
As expected, Zhuyan's here.

11:07.750 --> 11:09.180
Stay close, Lifei.

11:44.590 --> 11:45.260
Xiguang,

11:45.940 --> 11:47.660
what hexagram did you just divine?

11:49.350 --> 11:50.210
I didn't even do any divination.

11:50.710 --> 11:52.570
The straws snapped for no reason.

11:54.830 --> 11:55.780
Something's coming.

12:26.830 --> 12:27.450
Go now!

12:58.510 --> 12:59.330
Demon!

13:00.080 --> 13:01.660
So you're behind all this.

13:01.750 --> 13:04.020
Worthless immortals,

13:04.440 --> 13:07.610
you'll all rot in this tomb today!

13:12.510 --> 13:13.810
Demon, meet your end.

13:16.960 --> 13:18.180
Thank you, Immortal.

13:18.660 --> 13:20.060
You've lifted the tomb-sealing talisman

13:20.080 --> 13:23.300
that trapped my kin for centuries.

13:46.040 --> 13:46.690
It won't work.

13:47.870 --> 13:48.690
A formation looms overhead.

13:49.800 --> 13:51.210
Crafted by Wuyue Court's ancestors

13:52.200 --> 13:52.940
masterfully beyond compare,

13:53.440 --> 13:54.940
it's infused with the mystic arts of Qi Men Dun Jia,

13:56.510 --> 13:57.420
turning this place

13:57.440 --> 13:58.730
into an inescapable labyrinth.

14:04.280 --> 14:06.420
As one of those elders,

14:06.440 --> 14:07.210
can't Elder Cuixuan break it?

14:08.320 --> 14:09.090
Before coming here,

14:10.040 --> 14:11.380
I begged my master to let me

14:11.400 --> 14:12.660
read secret scrolls about the tomb.

14:13.110 --> 14:15.660
Elder Cuixuan came here thrice and returned gravely wounded.

14:17.920 --> 14:19.540
No one but the formation's creator

14:20.510 --> 14:21.730
can break it.

14:22.920 --> 14:24.140
Since he can't break it, did he lead us

14:24.160 --> 14:25.060
to die here?

14:26.320 --> 14:27.090
My master said

14:27.960 --> 14:28.970
Elder Cuixuan acts ruthlessly,

14:29.470 --> 14:30.420
risking everything without mercy

14:30.960 --> 14:31.970
for others or himself.

14:34.400 --> 14:36.300
Cultivation has stripped him of all compassion.

14:36.710 --> 14:37.610
His profound power

14:37.990 --> 14:39.330
lets him survive such gambles,

14:39.350 --> 14:40.140
but what about us?

14:40.320 --> 14:41.060
Are we disposable pawns?

14:42.400 --> 14:43.900
No wonder Deng's divination failed.

14:47.200 --> 14:47.850
Don't fear.

14:54.080 --> 14:54.850
You'll live.

14:59.560 --> 15:00.570
We all will.

15:01.510 --> 15:02.330
My master said

15:02.920 --> 15:03.690
no poison or formation

15:03.710 --> 15:04.900
is unbreakable.

15:05.230 --> 15:06.330
I refuse to believe we're trapped forever.

15:06.680 --> 15:07.180
Right.

15:07.990 --> 15:08.940
Man-made barriers

15:09.470 --> 15:10.490
always have an exit.

15:15.470 --> 15:16.940
The Life Gate is located in Gen Palace.

15:19.200 --> 15:19.690
Come.

15:26.870 --> 15:27.380
Lifei.

15:33.080 --> 15:33.900
Run now.

15:34.870 --> 15:35.780
You're just an eyesore.

15:36.080 --> 15:37.090
I wouldn't rest in peace

15:37.350 --> 15:38.300
if we perish together.

15:38.710 --> 15:39.450
Just accept it.

15:39.750 --> 15:40.570
I'll never leave you.

15:41.160 --> 15:42.490
Have you lost your mind?

15:56.920 --> 15:57.900
You're corrupted by a demon spirit.

15:58.750 --> 16:01.330
We need to purge the demonic energy inside you.

16:15.320 --> 16:16.420
You got corrupted too.

16:17.110 --> 16:18.380
Why channel your spirit energy to me?

16:26.680 --> 16:27.570
Save it for yourself.

16:28.350 --> 16:29.090
Shut up.

16:40.040 --> 16:40.610
Lifei.

16:47.110 --> 16:49.090
I never thought we'd die side by side.

16:50.110 --> 16:51.570
I'll die with regret.

16:53.960 --> 16:55.060
I thought that if I practiced hard,

16:57.110 --> 16:58.260
I could keep you safe,

16:59.470 --> 17:02.570
yet we ended up here.

17:03.960 --> 17:05.090
I'm nothing but a jinx.

17:05.750 --> 17:07.610
Why dwell on that now?

17:08.920 --> 17:10.490
You acted for Lu

17:10.920 --> 17:12.140
and had no choice.

17:12.140 --> 17:15.070
笙ｪThe warmth within my arms笙ｪ

17:15.070 --> 17:16.690
Have you forgiven me?

17:16.690 --> 17:19.070
笙ｪI can no longer hold on to笙ｪ

17:19.340 --> 17:20.180
Not yet.

17:20.180 --> 17:21.510
笙ｪIn the cold night, how can I笙ｪ

17:21.510 --> 17:22.340
So,

17:23.030 --> 17:24.420
once we die...

17:24.420 --> 17:25.710
笙ｪKeep you warm until sunrise?笙ｪ

17:25.710 --> 17:26.970
And reach Naihe Bridge...

17:26.970 --> 17:28.600
笙ｪMy heartbeat freezes笙ｪ

17:28.600 --> 17:30.620
We must drink the Forgetting Soup.

17:30.620 --> 17:31.840
笙ｪI can no longer tell you笙ｪ

17:31.840 --> 17:33.580
Make sure we never cross paths in the next life.

17:33.890 --> 17:36.600
笙ｪLooking you in the eyes, I cannot笙ｪ

17:36.600 --> 17:37.450
Got it?

17:37.450 --> 17:39.990
笙ｪUtter that line笙ｪ

17:39.990 --> 17:40.770
I won't.

17:40.770 --> 17:42.490
笙ｪKnowing love and hate笙ｪ

17:42.810 --> 17:46.730
笙ｪPain and wounds cannot be stopped笙ｪ

17:48.090 --> 17:49.690
笙ｪI still linger on笙ｪ

17:50.090 --> 17:52.400
笙ｪUnwilling to let go of every inch of our past笙ｪ

17:52.400 --> 17:53.820
I'll never drink it.

17:54.690 --> 17:58.200
笙ｪLast night's stars cast faint glimmers笙ｪ

17:58.200 --> 17:59.860
You've been a substitute this life,

18:00.990 --> 18:02.660
fleeing for your life since ten.

18:03.100 --> 18:04.290
Homeless,

18:04.790 --> 18:05.900
starving,

18:07.400 --> 18:09.140
living worse off than me.

18:09.850 --> 18:11.530
笙ｪKnowing right and wrong笙ｪ

18:11.890 --> 18:13.360
笙ｪBlack and gray are all illusions笙ｪ

18:13.360 --> 18:14.450
What's there

18:14.470 --> 18:15.940
for you to cling to?

18:17.510 --> 18:19.100
Drink it and be reborn sooner.

18:20.790 --> 18:21.730
In this life,

18:21.730 --> 18:23.410
笙ｪRunning relentlessly without regret笙ｪ

18:23.790 --> 18:24.690
I was treated unfairly.

18:24.690 --> 18:28.090
笙ｪThe storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way笙ｪ

18:29.030 --> 18:30.450
Yet life hasn't been entirely cruel.

18:31.720 --> 18:35.070
笙ｪLeaping straight into that heartbreaking past笙ｪ

18:35.070 --> 18:36.050
I have Lu

18:37.710 --> 18:38.340
and...

18:38.340 --> 18:42.580
笙ｪJust to keep you safe笙ｪ

18:50.440 --> 18:51.210
And you.

18:52.030 --> 18:53.180
I'm really lucky enough.

18:54.000 --> 18:57.690
笙ｪMy breath is about to stop笙ｪ

18:58.070 --> 19:01.320
笙ｪThose hands can no longer hold yours笙ｪ

19:01.680 --> 19:02.290
Truth is...

19:02.290 --> 19:04.310
笙ｪThrough the future snow, wind, and fog笙ｪ

19:04.310 --> 19:05.660
I don't want to forget you either.

19:05.680 --> 19:07.760
笙ｪWho will be there by your side?笙ｪ

19:08.120 --> 19:10.990
笙ｪI smile as it ends笙ｪ

19:10.990 --> 19:13.210
I traveled nonstop with my master since childhood...

19:13.210 --> 19:14.470
笙ｪAfraid that you might cry for me笙ｪ

19:14.470 --> 19:15.860
Never growing close to anyone.

19:15.930 --> 19:18.600
笙ｪQuietly, I turn into a sky lantern笙ｪ

19:18.600 --> 19:20.660
You're the first one to get close to me...

19:20.660 --> 19:22.450
笙ｪTo light your way through the night笙ｪ

19:23.340 --> 19:24.900
And the one I care for most

19:26.200 --> 19:27.690
besides my master.

19:30.920 --> 19:31.860
I was furious...

19:32.130 --> 19:34.840
笙ｪUnwilling to let go of every inch of our past笙ｪ

19:34.840 --> 19:36.340
Because I trusted you,

19:37.710 --> 19:39.100
but you lied to me.

19:39.100 --> 19:41.090
笙ｪLast night's stars cast faint glimmers笙ｪ

19:41.370 --> 19:44.330
笙ｪBut we thought nothing of it笙ｪ

19:45.510 --> 19:46.340
Still,

19:46.340 --> 19:48.090
笙ｪWith a heartbroken cry笙ｪ

19:48.400 --> 19:50.490
when you took my pain away...

19:50.490 --> 19:51.570
笙ｪI wish you well笙ｪ

19:53.200 --> 19:54.250
My heart broken.

19:55.920 --> 19:57.970
I feared for you when you

19:58.680 --> 19:59.690
shielded me from harm.

19:59.690 --> 20:00.850
笙ｪYou're still screaming笙ｪ

20:01.510 --> 20:02.340
Now...

20:02.340 --> 20:04.160
笙ｪRunning relentlessly without regret笙ｪ

20:04.160 --> 20:06.100
I understand the line from the storybook.

20:06.100 --> 20:08.960
笙ｪThe storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way笙ｪ

20:08.960 --> 20:10.100
Love blooms unawares.

20:10.520 --> 20:12.840
笙ｪTorn inside, still I burn bright笙ｪ

20:12.840 --> 20:13.770
Deepening without end.

20:13.770 --> 20:19.800
笙ｪWith the light from my fingertips, I build a paradise笙ｪ

20:20.520 --> 20:24.080
笙ｪTo wander with you笙ｪ

20:39.640 --> 20:40.420
Xiuyuan!

20:42.680 --> 20:43.530
Xiuyuan!

23:02.750 --> 23:04.380
Demon chants?

23:05.640 --> 23:06.580
Could it be...?

23:36.790 --> 23:37.450
Lifei,

23:37.960 --> 23:39.010
why is your spirit power so faint?

23:39.710 --> 23:40.620
What's wrong?

23:41.310 --> 23:42.140
Where is Lei?

23:52.510 --> 23:53.050
Watch out!

24:11.310 --> 24:12.100
It's Demon Lord!

24:13.100 --> 24:14.250
Demon Lord Yecha has revived!

25:06.920 --> 25:08.180
Lifei, it's too dangerous here.

25:08.310 --> 25:09.050
Let's leave at once.

25:12.750 --> 25:13.340
Lifei!

25:43.070 --> 25:43.820
Xiuyuan,

25:48.750 --> 25:49.860
it's Lifei.

25:55.030 --> 25:55.730
Xiuyuan,

25:57.440 --> 25:58.770
don't you recognize me?

26:09.230 --> 26:10.210
Xiuyuan.

26:38.470 --> 26:39.340
Master,

26:39.470 --> 26:42.340
why do those spirits keep pestering me?

26:42.680 --> 26:44.340
You're different from others.

26:44.640 --> 26:47.580
They crave your hair

26:47.600 --> 26:49.140
and blood.

27:06.440 --> 27:10.120
笙ｪI trade all the mortal world's splendor笙ｪ

27:10.440 --> 27:12.940
笙ｪFor a fleeting moment with you笙ｪ

27:13.400 --> 27:16.720
笙ｪOur fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting笙ｪ

27:16.960 --> 27:19.160
笙ｪThe hardest bond to balance笙ｪ

27:20.200 --> 27:23.680
笙ｪObsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise笙ｪ

27:24.400 --> 27:26.760
笙ｪLove sprouts again in this lifetime笙ｪ

27:27.360 --> 27:28.880
笙ｪNo calamity can rival笙ｪ

27:29.280 --> 27:32.320
笙ｪThe lingering thread of a fragrance笙ｪ

27:34.460 --> 27:37.940
笙ｪWith you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand笙ｪ

27:38.700 --> 27:40.940
笙ｪWithered branches burst into bloom笙ｪ

27:41.380 --> 27:44.420
笙ｪHand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda笙ｪ

27:45.060 --> 27:47.340
笙ｪIn fine robes on galloping horses笙ｪ

27:48.140 --> 27:51.620
笙ｪAlways, at the very end of obsession笙ｪ

27:51.980 --> 27:54.260
笙ｪComes that one moment of softness笙ｪ

27:54.780 --> 27:57.740
笙ｪBetrayed by all, I still笙ｪ

27:58.460 --> 28:00.660
笙ｪReign supreme笙ｪ

28:01.680 --> 28:04.960
笙ｪWith you, we melt into mist and haze笙ｪ

28:11.280 --> 28:14.520
笙ｪI trade the highest heaven and endless clouds笙ｪ

28:15.240 --> 28:17.520
笙ｪFor a fleeting moment with you笙ｪ

28:18.120 --> 28:21.320
笙ｪPierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on笙ｪ

28:21.520 --> 28:23.960
笙ｪYet I remain silent笙ｪ

28:24.800 --> 28:28.360
笙ｪDeep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream笙ｪ

28:29.200 --> 28:31.440
笙ｪIn the distant night, bitterness blooms笙ｪ

28:32.440 --> 28:33.960
笙ｪThe grand chapter is rewritten笙ｪ

28:34.360 --> 28:37.280
笙ｪStartling the whole world笙ｪ

28:38.840 --> 28:42.360
笙ｪWith you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand笙ｪ

28:43.040 --> 28:45.800
笙ｪWithered branches burst into bloom笙ｪ

28:46.000 --> 28:49.120
笙ｪHand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda笙ｪ

28:49.560 --> 28:52.200
笙ｪIn fine robes on galloping horses笙ｪ

28:52.440 --> 28:56.320
笙ｪAlways, at the very end of obsession笙ｪ

28:56.560 --> 28:59.600
笙ｪComes that one moment of softness笙ｪ

28:59.680 --> 29:02.560
笙ｪBetrayed by all, I still笙ｪ

29:03.240 --> 29:05.720
笙ｪReign supreme笙ｪ

29:06.920 --> 29:10.520
笙ｪIf the seal can't be broken, then let it go笙ｪ

29:11.080 --> 29:13.520
笙ｪWhere the heart finds peace, there is home笙ｪ

29:13.640 --> 29:15.560
笙ｪSide by side, we fly through seas of clouds笙ｪ

29:15.720 --> 29:17.080
笙ｪBreak through the waves笙ｪ

29:17.520 --> 29:20.000
笙ｪThe heart's ocean knows no shore笙ｪ

29:20.200 --> 29:24.040
笙ｪAlways, at the very end of fate笙ｪ

29:24.280 --> 29:27.040
笙ｪComes that one moment of defiance笙ｪ

29:27.440 --> 29:30.760
笙ｪIn the human world or above, like flowing water笙ｪ

29:31.400 --> 29:33.640
笙ｪAnd falling petals笙ｪ

29:34.230 --> 29:35.010
Lifei!

29:35.040 --> 29:38.520
笙ｪLet this fleeting life be whatever it may笙ｪ

29:54.160 --> 29:55.100
Fish!

29:58.990 --> 29:59.620
Run!

30:23.990 --> 30:24.860
Don't overthink it.

30:26.200 --> 30:27.250
You're so weak

30:27.880 --> 30:28.860
that you were possessed by the demonic energy,

30:29.640 --> 30:30.940
like being haunted.

30:31.360 --> 30:32.340
It's nothing serious.

30:52.680 --> 30:53.340
Don't

30:54.120 --> 30:55.580
misinterpret what I did.

30:55.920 --> 30:57.690
I was only saving you.

31:05.230 --> 31:06.050
This scent...

31:11.440 --> 31:12.100
This way.

31:42.600 --> 31:43.140
What's wrong?

32:28.990 --> 32:30.490
The aura of the Divine Tree.

32:32.640 --> 32:34.620
It's really here.

32:42.270 --> 32:43.340
I think I saw it

32:45.200 --> 32:46.340
somewhere before.

32:54.990 --> 32:56.210
This scent is the same as Lifei's.

32:58.680 --> 32:59.940
Could I be Yecha?

33:03.510 --> 33:04.010
No,

33:04.960 --> 33:06.100
I've never hurt Lifei.

33:11.030 --> 33:11.690
Xiuyuan,

33:12.270 --> 33:14.010
this wound looks like it was torn off.

33:20.030 --> 33:20.940
What are you doing?

33:32.640 --> 33:34.580
The aura is gone.

34:40.400 --> 34:41.010
Lifei!

34:41.880 --> 34:42.570
Lifei.

34:43.110 --> 34:43.780
Lifei.

34:47.800 --> 34:48.900
Where have you two been?

34:49.360 --> 34:50.010
Are you alright?

34:56.840 --> 34:57.530
We're fine.

35:04.070 --> 35:04.570
Master,

35:05.110 --> 35:06.610
the tomb sank into the sea,

35:06.990 --> 35:08.530
so the demon threat should be gone.

35:09.240 --> 35:10.420
The White Cliff lies in ruins,

35:11.360 --> 35:13.740
yet we found no trace of the Demon Lord's corpse.

35:14.360 --> 35:16.010
I cannot rest easy.

35:16.990 --> 35:18.530
This tomb disaster means

35:19.280 --> 35:21.300
the demon clan will strike again.

35:22.630 --> 35:24.260
Send word to all immortal sects

35:24.720 --> 35:26.220
across the nine states to prepare.

35:26.760 --> 35:27.300
Understood.

35:50.190 --> 35:50.860
Lifei.

35:56.990 --> 35:59.260
I told you the hexagram Earth Over Mountain, Modesty was ill-omened.

35:59.670 --> 36:00.450
Earth over mountain

36:00.590 --> 36:01.130
signals a great shock.

36:01.840 --> 36:03.530
The White Cliff collapsed.

36:08.190 --> 36:08.900
Do you think

36:09.670 --> 36:11.900
Demon Lord Yecha perished?

36:18.360 --> 36:20.700
I once thought my master's tales

36:21.590 --> 36:23.740
of Yecha were overblown,

36:24.110 --> 36:25.170
but now I know

36:26.720 --> 36:28.530
they were not.

36:29.110 --> 36:29.900
You know what?

36:30.150 --> 36:31.610
When his gaze fell on me,

36:31.990 --> 36:33.820
my legs froze.

36:36.030 --> 36:37.300
Luckily,

36:38.220 --> 36:39.820
he just revived

36:40.190 --> 36:41.170
with power yet to return.

36:41.880 --> 36:42.940
Otherwise...

36:45.670 --> 36:46.490
Xiguang,

36:48.510 --> 36:50.300
did Yecha truly slaughter countless souls?

36:51.030 --> 36:52.700
He slaughtered countless people,

36:53.400 --> 36:55.130
like a nightmare for all the immortal sects.

37:13.760 --> 37:14.380
Xiguang,

37:15.030 --> 37:16.300
have you seen

37:16.960 --> 37:18.780
a huge transparent fish?

37:21.840 --> 37:23.300
There's a fish in the Northern Ocean

37:23.440 --> 37:24.780
named Kun.

37:25.220 --> 37:26.420
Its size

37:26.880 --> 37:28.010
is beyond imagination.

37:28.590 --> 37:29.820
You saw something

37:30.840 --> 37:31.610
no mortal has ever witnessed.

37:32.360 --> 37:33.820
Legends say the Kun fish comes from overseas.

37:34.030 --> 37:34.940
It's a sacred spirit

37:35.510 --> 37:36.820
and is rarely seen.

37:56.360 --> 37:57.650
Are those rock piles

37:58.110 --> 37:59.940
linked to Master?

38:00.880 --> 38:01.740
Whose severed arm

38:02.550 --> 38:03.610
was it?

38:11.960 --> 38:12.820
Jiang Lifei.

38:16.280 --> 38:17.820
Why come here alone?

38:19.360 --> 38:19.940
I lost

38:20.590 --> 38:22.220
my Xiaying Sword,

38:22.800 --> 38:24.860
and it was forged specially by my master.

38:25.110 --> 38:26.170
I dare not return

38:26.760 --> 38:28.490
if I can't find it.

38:31.990 --> 38:33.010
Where did you drop it?

38:34.700 --> 38:35.700
I don't know.

38:36.070 --> 38:37.050
Everything was a mess yesterday.

38:37.590 --> 38:39.570
Those demons kept chasing me,

38:40.320 --> 38:42.650
and I don't know where I dropped it.

38:47.800 --> 38:49.340
Where is it?

38:55.630 --> 38:57.170
Yangling told me

38:57.550 --> 38:59.900
you were there when Yecha appeared,

39:00.220 --> 39:02.740
but he lost sight of you during the escape.

39:06.150 --> 39:07.490
Where did you go afterward?

39:11.990 --> 39:13.300
My cultivation is weak,

39:14.220 --> 39:17.050
and Qin vanished at once.

39:28.510 --> 39:29.220
Found it!

39:33.110 --> 39:33.900
I found it.

39:41.510 --> 39:42.650
Yecha has returned,

39:43.030 --> 39:44.300
and the demon clan stirs restlessly.

39:44.700 --> 39:45.900
Facing the Sea Calamity,

39:46.150 --> 39:47.610
the Central Plains face grave danger.

39:48.360 --> 39:50.780
I hereby invite all immortals

39:50.800 --> 39:52.650
to Duanming City by the East Sea

39:52.990 --> 39:55.090
for the Shanhai Gathering.

39:56.110 --> 39:59.220
Immortal Cuixuan, we await your arrival with your disciples.

40:01.450 --> 40:03.640
[Duanming City]

40:13.360 --> 40:14.970
Aren't people here afraid of spirits?

40:14.990 --> 40:15.860
Not at all.

40:16.150 --> 40:18.170
Sea Sects excel at taming them.

40:18.590 --> 40:19.220
Every spirit

40:19.280 --> 40:20.820
you see here

40:20.840 --> 40:22.340
serves humans.

40:22.670 --> 40:24.130
So in Duanming City,

40:24.280 --> 40:25.650
humans and monsters coexist.

40:25.960 --> 40:27.420
It's a unique sight of the Central Plains.

40:32.840 --> 40:33.820
Elder Cuixuan,

40:34.440 --> 40:35.220
Qin,

40:36.470 --> 40:37.860
my father awaits you

40:37.880 --> 40:39.340
at Luxin Hall of Wanxian Sect.

40:39.590 --> 40:40.050
This way.

40:40.510 --> 40:41.700
Many thanks, Ms. Shen.

40:47.880 --> 40:48.490
Lifei,

40:48.960 --> 40:50.940
congratulations on joining Wuyue Court as you wished.

40:51.510 --> 40:53.420
Credit goes to the masters' teaching.

40:54.700 --> 40:55.450
Where's Mr. Mo?

40:55.760 --> 40:57.090
Fearing you'd take Yanfan away,

40:57.440 --> 40:59.340
we sent him on an overseas task early.

41:02.070 --> 41:04.170
Didn't you want to break the Fragrance Bond?

41:04.700 --> 41:05.260
What?

41:05.630 --> 41:06.420
Made up now?

41:08.550 --> 41:09.220
Where's Gelin?

41:09.510 --> 41:11.860
She left on business with Lu Li.

41:12.150 --> 41:13.340
She said

41:13.360 --> 41:14.340
she'll come to you later.

41:14.920 --> 41:16.340
Will you head to Wanxian Sect with me,

41:16.360 --> 41:17.300
or wander around?

41:17.700 --> 41:18.260
Walk around.

41:22.760 --> 41:23.380
Lifei,

41:23.670 --> 41:24.450
want candied hawthorns?

41:24.880 --> 41:25.860
Fine, you take them.

41:26.960 --> 41:28.010
Sir, two, please.

41:28.470 --> 41:28.860
Okay.

41:29.280 --> 41:30.420
- How much? - Here you are.

41:33.510 --> 41:34.530
There's an aromatic shop.

41:34.920 --> 41:36.300
Zhaomin would love it.

41:42.670 --> 41:44.130
You only care about her, not me.

41:52.360 --> 41:54.650
[Wanxian Sect]
Yecha'd been slain by ancient immortals,

41:55.070 --> 41:57.260
yet revived with evil arts,

41:57.470 --> 41:58.970
filled with raging resentment.

41:59.990 --> 42:02.650
Recent disturbances in the mountain-sea barrier

42:03.220 --> 42:06.050
are likely tied to his return.

42:06.320 --> 42:09.610
The barrier was built by Wuyue Court's ancestors.

42:09.990 --> 42:11.420
A catastrophe looms.

42:11.840 --> 42:14.940
We must protect the barrier at all costs.

42:16.150 --> 42:17.420
Since the barrier lies off the East Sea,

42:17.470 --> 42:18.940
let disciples of both sects

42:19.220 --> 42:21.130
patrol nearby islands

42:21.150 --> 42:22.900
during this gathering

42:22.960 --> 42:24.010
to root out dangers.

42:24.440 --> 42:26.650
Humans and spirits coexist here.

42:27.630 --> 42:30.220
Shen, do not let your guard down.

42:41.070 --> 42:41.740
Tongzhou?

42:42.200 --> 42:42.510
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.510 --> 42:44.720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:57.500 --> 43:01.020
笙ｪThe warmth within my arms笙ｪ

43:01.180 --> 43:04.700
笙ｪI can no longer hold on to笙ｪ

43:04.820 --> 43:08.340
笙ｪIn the cold night, how can I笙ｪ

43:08.460 --> 43:11.940
笙ｪKeep you warm until sunrise?笙ｪ

43:11.940 --> 43:15.580
笙ｪMy heartbeat freezes笙ｪ

43:15.980 --> 43:19.260
笙ｪI can no longer tell you笙ｪ

43:19.380 --> 43:22.900
笙ｪLooking you in the eyes, I cannot笙ｪ

43:22.940 --> 43:25.940
笙ｪUtter that line笙ｪ

43:26.100 --> 43:28.140
笙ｪKnowing love and hate笙ｪ

43:28.220 --> 43:32.620
笙ｪPain and wounds cannot be stopped笙ｪ

43:33.340 --> 43:35.420
笙ｪI still linger on笙ｪ

43:35.580 --> 43:39.860
笙ｪUnwilling to let go of every inch of our past笙ｪ

43:40.020 --> 43:44.540
笙ｪLast night's stars cast faint glimmers笙ｪ

43:44.620 --> 43:48.140
笙ｪBut we thought nothing of it笙ｪ

43:48.220 --> 43:51.660
笙ｪWith a heartbroken cry笙ｪ

43:51.940 --> 43:55.180
笙ｪI wish you well笙ｪ

43:55.340 --> 43:57.060
笙ｪKnowing right and wrong笙ｪ

43:57.220 --> 44:01.900
笙ｪBlack and gray are all illusions笙ｪ

44:02.500 --> 44:04.580
笙ｪYou're still screaming笙ｪ

44:04.740 --> 44:09.220
笙ｪRunning relentlessly without regret笙ｪ

44:09.340 --> 44:13.820
笙ｪThe storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way笙ｪ

44:14.060 --> 44:17.020
笙ｪA final farewell left on the cliff笙ｪ

44:17.140 --> 44:19.020
笙ｪLeaping straight into笙ｪ

44:19.140 --> 44:23.900
笙ｪThat heartbreaking past笙ｪ

44:24.140 --> 44:27.660
笙ｪJust to keep you safe笙ｪ

44:34.100 --> 44:37.420
笙ｪMy breath is about to stop笙ｪ

44:37.540 --> 44:41.060
笙ｪThose hands can no longer hold yours笙ｪ

44:41.180 --> 44:44.620
笙ｪThrough the future snow, wind, and fog笙ｪ

44:44.780 --> 44:47.980
笙ｪWho will be there by your side?笙ｪ

44:48.100 --> 44:51.820
笙ｪI smile as it ends笙ｪ

44:51.980 --> 44:55.620
笙ｪAfraid that you might cry for me笙ｪ

44:55.820 --> 44:59.220
笙ｪQuietly, I turn into a sky lantern笙ｪ

44:59.380 --> 45:02.500
笙ｪTo light your way through the night笙ｪ

45:02.580 --> 45:04.620
笙ｪKnowing love and hate笙ｪ

45:04.700 --> 45:09.100
笙ｪPain and wounds cannot be stopped笙ｪ

45:09.860 --> 45:11.900
笙ｪI still linger on笙ｪ

45:12.060 --> 45:16.340
笙ｪUnwilling to let go of every inch of our past笙ｪ

45:16.500 --> 45:21.020
笙ｪThe storm looms, yet I stand in its way笙ｪ

45:21.100 --> 45:24.300
笙ｪTorn inside, still I burn bright笙ｪ

45:24.500 --> 45:26.460
笙ｪWith the light from my fingertips笙ｪ

45:26.540 --> 45:30.940
笙ｪI build a paradise笙ｪ

45:31.100 --> 45:34.580
笙ｪTo wander with you笙ｪ
